description: Donald's imagination takes Daisy and his nephews on an interesting journey back to the eighteenth century. His creative storytelling speaks of yet another mysterious version of the legend about what really happened to The Man in the Iron Mask.

volume.name: Donald Duck In The Duck In The Iron Mask

description: The new movie about vampires is making all the girls in Duckburg dream of romance! Daisy Duck and Brigitta aren't immune to the mysterious charm of vampires, and they begin writing a romantic story with vampires set in their very own city?

It's summertime and everyone in Duckburg seems to be out of the city on vacation! Everyone except Rockerduck, who's hard at work trying to beat Scrooge out of the top spot on Duckburg's Richest List? Will he get the revenge he seeks? And even if he does, who will bear witness?

volume.name: Rockerduck And The Summer Of Revenge

description: Uncle Scrooge has become very generous... maybe too generous! What's happened? An extremely rare mosquito has bitten Scrooge, and has changed his personality, to the point where his financial situation becomes quite precarious! But can Donald Duck help him?

volume.name: Scrooge McDuck And The Riversquito Bite

description: Fethry Duck and Moby Duck are determined to retrieve all the missing pieces of a chess set that is in the bottom of the sea off the coast of Duckport! But they are not the only ones who want to take possession of the complete chess set... Azimuth and his henchmen are maneuvering Fethry and Moby into checkmate!

volume.name: The Stories Of The Bay: Your King Is In Check!

description: Donald Duck owes a fortune to creditors, with Uncle Scrooge at the head of the line. Seeing no way out, Donald wishes he could start over in a new life--an alternative life. But what happens when Donald's wish actually comes true... three times?

volume.name: Donald Duck And The Alternative Lives

description: What could happen to a duck whose TV is on the blink? The Evrons are threatening Earth... and only a Guardian of the Galaxy can thwart their plans! Check out the exciting story of how Donald Duck turns into Superduck!
name: Superhero Of The Day

description: The Evrons want to use the new theme park for their evil plans. Only Superduck is able to stop them, thanks to an incredible discovery!
name: Toyland

description: Something's going wrong in Duckburg: strange objects are coming from a parallel dimension. Superduck is the only answer to this terrible problem!
name: A Perfect World

description: The Money Bin... vanished? Scrooge McDuck kidnapped? And the Beagle Boys are not the ones responsible?! Mysterious supervillains are making their moves...
name: Prologue

description: The Ultradetector has been stolen! And whomever possesses this device will be able to find the hidden parts to the most dangerous weapon: the Ultramachine! Eega Beeva has assembled the greatest superheroes from Duckburg to form the super team, Ultraheroes! Will they be able to solve this mystery before it's too late?
name: Gathering

description: It's a fight to the finish when Super Goof and the Ultra Heroes cross horns with the Sinister 7 over possession of the precious Ultrapods... the key to World Domination! But with the Ultra Heroes behind on their training and slacking off, things don't look very promising. Can Super Goof and Mickey Mouse rally the heroes and defeat the Sinister 7 before all of the Ultrapods fall into the wrong hands?
name: Brain and Muscle

description: The race between the Ultraheroes and the Sinister 7 to possess the powerful Ultrapod is still in full throttle. But things take a turn for the worse for the Heroes when Lucky Clover throws a fight to try to gain fame and fortune for himself.
name: Fame and Fortune

description: In the time of legends, wizards, and heroes, Mickey Mouse, Goofy, and Donald Duck are three brave wizards off to challenge their enemies in the biggest magic tournament of all time! Will the Wizards of Mickey be able to recover the Diamagics?
name: The Great Tournament

description: The Wizards of Mickey have triumphed in their first challenge! Will they find the scroll and win the contest, or will they be defeated by Alterus Band?
name: The Dolmen Swamp

description: The Wizards of Mickey must go on a mission to free Mickey's master, Nereus, the wise sorcerer who was captured by the Lord of Deception and his Black Phantom team! To do this they must fight dragons to protect the Diamagics, ancient dragon magical secrets! Along the way, they befriend Fafnir, the little dragon who causes things to take an unexpected turn!
name: The Secret of the Great Crown

description: It's vacation time in Mouseton and Arizona Goof convinces Mickey Mouse to follow him on a long journey into the deepest jungle, heading towards an ancient temple! But what's the real goal of the expedition and what is Arizona searching for so desperately?

volume.name: Arizona Goof and the Risky Adventure

description: A magic mirror carries Mickey Mouse into Wasteland, the magic world created for forgotten characters, where Mickey Mouse meets up with Oswald again! After so many years, the day of reckoning has arrived: Will Mickey Mouse win the battle against Phantom Blot, make amends for his mistake, and win Oswald's trust?
name: GN

description: Oswald the Lucky Rabbit and his animatronic friends, Donald Duck and Goofy, confront a furious Clocktower that is spreading dirt through Wasteland... Plus: Anything can happen in OsTown: Oswald the Lucky Rabbit has to find something that is very difficult to lose...

Magica's enchanting parties are big hit among her peers. But, when she poses as a party planner for Scrooge McDuck's big event for the Maharajah, will she finally be able to use her magical talents to get the one dime, or will she be left disenchanted?

volume.name: Magica De Spell and the Enchanted Party

description: Enter the cruel and treacherous world of the Wild West, where bandits abound and robberies are a fact of life. Mickey Kid and Goofy Six-Shots are bounty hunters on the search for Phantom Bobby and his gang of thieves, but betrayal awaits? Who is the culprit?

Experience the magic and a world of evil stepmothers, friendly mice and fairy godmothers! Follow Cinderella as she discovers that whatever she believes in with all her heart can come true... even when all hope seems lost!

In ancient times, in the court of King Stefan and Queen Leah, everybody is excited about the birth of Aurora, the princess they had been longing for. Three good fairies want to give the baby three special gifts, but before the last gift is offered, the wicked witch Maleficent casts a curse on Aurora: on her sixteenth birthday, she will prick her finger on the spindle of a spinning wheel and die! The third fairy manages to weaken the curse: the princess won't die, but will fall into a deep sleep, from which she will awake only with true love's kiss!

Long ago, there lived a beautiful and cheerful young maiden named Snow White. She lived in a castle, and had to work hard everyday. But, the castle's evil Queen found out that Snow White had replaced her as the most beautiful woman in the land. Mad with jealousy, the Queen sentenced her to death. But Snow White escaped, and was rescued by seven wonderful dwarfs. But the Queen's jealousy had now turned into rage...

volume.name: Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs

description: A mysterious tower hidden in the woods in a faraway kingdom; a king and a queen searching for their kidnapped daughter; and a beautiful girl whose golden hair has incredible magical powers... this is no ordinary fairy tale! After 18 years spent locked in a tower, Rapunzel rebels against the woman she believes to be her mother and plans to go out--even if it's just once. But a chance encounter with a charming and gallant thief, Flynn Rider, leads her to discover the truth about her origins...and about her heart!

A talented and ambitious race car like Lightning McQueen has many great plans for his future, starting with becoming the first rookie to win the prestigious Piston Cup! But while McQueen makes his way to the big race, he finds himself stuck in Radiator Springs, a small desert town that time has forgotten, and which Lightning would also like to forget. As Lightning gets to know the many quirky cars in this town--including the grumpy Doc with a mysterious past and the sleek, sporty Sally--he finds that his former priorities might be shifting. When race day arrives at last, millions of fans across the globe will see the Piston Cup end in a really unexpected way?

Relive this heroic tale of a fearful father who embarks on a dangerous journey through the deep ocean to rescue his only son, Nemo. Watch as both father and son learn to trust themselves and each other in this daring adventure and laugh with Dory, the adorable and forgetful friend who proves that friendship can be found in unexpected places if you just keep swimming.

A new adventure awaits the famous superhero family, the Incredibles! Fifteen years ago, Mr. Incredible and his wife, Elastigirl, put away their uniforms to become Bob and Helen Parr, parents of wonderful children! But when a new menace comes along, Bob is contacted by a government secret agency that asks him to go back to being Mr. Incredible...

Relive the story of Simba, a young cub who has yet to learn his place in the circle of life! Follow his journey through treacherous lands with unexpected friends and deceitful enemies, culminating with the chance to confront his past and become the kind of king his father would be proud of!

It's Andy's birthday, and as he starts opening his presents, his old toys fear the worst: Will they be replaced? Woody is confident that they won't be--that is, until Buzz Lightyear comes along and seems to steal Woody's cherished place in Andy's heart. Is there room for two favorite toys on Andy's bed? And is Buzz Lightyear as special as he thinks he is, or will Woody burst his bubble?

The MANCHESTER GODS dread URBAN PANTHESISM arises in the north of Otherworld, the British Subconscious! Don't look panicked. We just mean "Civil War." A Civil War that Asgardia refuses to interfere in. Publicly. Behind the scenes, Loki is a one-man intervention force. Also: Secret mission from Hela!

COLLECTING: JOURNEY INTO MYSTERY 639-641, THE MIGHTY THOR ANNUAL 1.
name: TPB

volume.name: Journey Into Mystery: The Manchester Gods

description: A ghost, a treasure map and piracy await Donald Duck and his nephews in this high seas adventure! Join them, as they battle the Beagle Boys and Uncle Scrooge for their lives, all in the search for... Treasure Island!

volume.name: Donald Duck and the Treasure Island

description: A ghost, a treasure map and piracy await Donald Duck and his nephews in this high seas adventure! Join them, as they battle the Beagle Boys and Uncle Scrooge for their lives, all in the search for... Treasure Island!

volume.name: Donald Duck and the Treasure Island

description: He is brave, smart and intelligent: he is DoubleDuck! The spy agency "so secret it has not even a name" needs the help of its best man, Donald Duck!
The Agency so secret that it doesn't even have a name has a case for DoubleDuck. Retrieve a stolen laptop containing highly sensitive before it gets into the wrong hands. But is it too late?

A life of espionage has not been as glamorous and exciting as Donald had expected, until now! Follow DoubleDuck as he strives to save himself and his fellow agents from certain death in the ultimate double agent betrayal in the secret agency's history. In a world of lies and deception, the only truth he can trust is that no one is to be trusted! Will DoubleDuck figure out who the traitors are, before it's too late?

Join Mickey Mouse and Goofy on this adventure of mythical proportions in a dimension where they must venture into unknown places in search for the Lost Sword of Ice in the Land of Giants! The welfare of the people of Ululand depends on it...but will they be successful?

volume.name: Mickey Mouse In The Sword Of Ice

description: Mickey and Goofy must seek the assistance of the Queen of Hel in order to reach the Enchanted Forest! But the Prince of Fogs has other plans for our heroic friends: Goofy falls under a spell as the deadline for finding the Lost Sword quickly approaches! What will happen next?

volume.name: Mickey Mouse In The Sword Of Ice

description: Mickey and Goofy find an unlikely ally in the Land of Trolls to help them on their quest, but first they must find the Land of Giants and recover the sword! The Prince of Fogs is closer than ever! Will our heroes overcome the dark forces of evil? Find out in the stunning conclusion of this adventurous saga!

volume.name: Mickey Mouse In The Sword Of Ice

description: Mickey Mouse and Peg-Leg Pete aren't the best of friends. It hasn't been the same since they both worked on a riverboat, a riverboat that is now? well, at the bottom of the river. But now, after years of waiting, the shipwreck is finally visible and ready to be explored.

volume.name: Mickey Mouse In The River Of Time

description: Mickey Mouse and Peg-Leg Pete both worked on a riverboat that sunk and ended up at the bottom of a river. Now Mickey wants to return to the boat he loved to find out what caused the sinking that ended his maritime career. The only problem is, he's not the only one interested in what might be found in the wreck?

volume.name: Mickey Mouse In The River Of Time

description: Mickey and Goofy go back to sixth century Camelot to uncover the mystery of King Arthur and his round table! Think you know the legend? Join them on this adventure back in time and discover what these legendary characters were really like.. you may be surprised by how much hasn't changed in 15 centuries!

volume.name: Mickey Mouse And The Knights Of The Round Table

description: Martians are landing on Earth and they don't seem very friendly! Only Mickey Mouse and Goofy can save our Planet...with some unexpected help!

volume.name: Mickey Mouse In War of the Worlds

description: A relaxing vacation for Donald Duckling turns soon into a dangerous adventure: two rascals manage to kidnap Donald and his friends! After escaping with a cunning trick, the little ducklings are on the road to Quacktown, risking an encounter with the terrible monster Sasquack?
name: The Secret of Sasquack

description: With the help of a gruff hermit, Donald Duckling and his friends managed to escape from their kidnappers, who are still on their trails! After a crash landing in a mountain forest, the ducklings come across another group of children... What is the mystery of this community hidden in the woods?
name: Ghosts From the Past

description: What could a small squad of British cooks do to escape when they were trapped in a huge forest, caught up in the massive German onslaught through France? Well, it was surprising what they could do when they were led by someone as crafty as Sergeant Mike Taylor!
name: Cook-House Heroes

description:
The little island of Dinara, off the coast of Yugoslavia, hardly knew there was a war on. Sure, they were under German occupation, but all that meant was a weekly visit from a section of infantrymen who were supposed to look out for suspicious happenings. And the only suspicious thing about Dinara was how much Stanislas Brod the innkeeper charged for his wine.

Yes, a pleasant little place, Dinara - until the day a certain strange object fell through the roof of Brod's inn‚Ä¶

His Flying Fortress shot full of holes, his co-pilot wounded, many of his crew dead, himself almost passing out from loss of blood‚Ä¶American bomber pilot Al Warner wondered why he'd given up the safer life of a newspaper photographer to dice with death in the hostile skies over Germany.

description: Collecting ALOT of LiH-strips.
name: The Huge Book of Hell

volume.name: Army of Darkness: Ashes 2 Ashes Director's Cut

description: With her existence on Earth erased from the minds of those who loved her, Augusta heads into the cosmic fog called The Swirl. But the road to Nowhere Island is dark and dangerous-and a mysterious Forever Wall lies ahead.
name: The Girl with the Umbrella, Book One Chapter Three: Nowhere Lost

description:
The secrets of the house‚Äîand dangers‚Äîare deepening with every passing hour!

Austin‚Äôs reappearance covered in blood and holding a tomahawk raises some questions concerning not just to WHERE his family is, but WHEN!
Contains : Wolverine and the X-Men (2011) #17-18

Detective Kelly is still seeking a clear perspective on Batman's July 4th battle at the baseball game. But will speaking directly to the Calendar Man help or hinder that effort? "What Happened Was?" part 2 of 3.
name: What Happened Was..., Part 2 of 3
Tutte le Avventure di Giuseppe Bergman
Dylan Dog: Una Voce dal Nulla
Il Primo Che Ride Lo Disintegro

description: "Chambre obscure" ("Dark Room") is a "thriller" in the manner of "Myst√®re de la chambre jaune" and the adventures of Ars√®ne Lupin. The story takes place in the suburbs of Paris in 1910 and played on the psychology of the characters while reflecting on the relationship between reality and fiction.

We plunge back with a vengeance in the mystery surrounding the theft of paintings Dambroise family. After three weeks in the family home, it is time for a free and independent woman like Alma back on the road. While the police actively seeking Mauritius, the butler on the run, a mysterious figure continues to roam around the house. But the departure of Alma will relaunch the investigation in an unexpected direction, forcing each of the protagonists and the arriving Inspector Leblanc to undergo an adventure of twists and turns, leading to the famous "Chambre Obscure" ...
